Local styles
============

To install LaTeX styles in a user's home directory, create the
following directory structure:

    ~/texmf
        tex
            latex

Drop the .sty files in the 'latex' directory. Finally, run the
following to generate the special ls-R index file:

    $ mktexlsr ~/texmf

Altogether, the following should be sufficient:

    $ mkdir -p ~/texmf/tex/latex
    $ cp /path/to/*.sty ~/texmf/tex/latex/.
    $ mktexlsr ~/texmf
